Title: CCLE.log2.read.count.matrix
Description: log2-transformed matrix containing expression of 56,318 genes in 1,019 cell lines provided in CCLE database

Title: CCLE.overlaps
Description: log2-transformed matrix containing expression of 56,318 genes in 51 cell lines present in both LINCS and CCLE databases

Title: CCLE.sample.meta
Description: data.frame containing cell lines name and tissue of origin from CCLE database

Title: CTRPv2.sensprof
Description: Cancer Therapeutics Response Portal (CTRP) data.frame containing AUC and IC50 for every drug-cell line pair

Title: EncoderDF
Description: a data.frame (64 features by 19127 samples) computed from autoEncoder for every sample in the OCTAD database

Title: cmpd_sets_ChemCluster
Description: list of compounds and their clusters based on chemical structures

Title: cmpd_sets_chembl_targets
Description: list of compounds and their targets presented in ChEMBL database

Title: cmpd_sets_mesh
Description: list of compounds and their associations with 662 pharmacological MeSH Terms provided in PubChem

Title: fda_drugs
Description: data.frame of FDA approved drugs containing name, target and clinical phase

Title: lincs_sig_info
Description: data.frame for LINCS signatures including experiment id, cell line used in the experiment, purturbagen name, purturbagen type, dose and time

Title: lincs_signatures
Description: Differential expression of 978 genes in 416,560 experiments

Title: merged_gene_info
Description: data.frame with the annotation of 75,078 genes which could be used for identifier mapping

Title: octad.LINCS.counts
Description: expression matrix of 965 genes and 19127 samples in OCTAD database (965 genes were profiled in LINCS)

Title: phenoDF
Description: data.frame with samples from the OCTAD database including tissue of origin, sample type (tumor-derived or healthy-derived), cancer, orginal source (e.g. TCGA), mutation and stage data if available

Title: random_gsea_score
Description: precomputed permutated gsea scores for chembl, mesh and ChemCluster databases that are used for drug enrichment analysis

Title: tsne
Description: 2 dimension tSNE for every sample in the OCTAD database along with sample.id, cancer type and source of the initial data

Title: octad.counts.and.tpm.h5
Description: expression (TPM and raw counts) matrix of 60,498 genes and 19,127 samples

Title: res_example.rda
Description: example of differential expression analysis of HCC vs adjacent liver for OCTAD performed on genes contained in LINCs database

Title: sRGES_example.rda
Description: example of RGES computed from DE analysis of HCC vs adjacent liver for OCTAD performed on genes contained in LINCs database
